{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "a1b2c3d4-tourky-portals",
		"name": "Tourky — Admin / Captain / Client APIs",
		"description": "Sanctum auth for three prefixed portals (`/api/admin`, `/api/captain`, `/api/client`).\n\n**Setup:** set `baseUrl` (e.g. `http://127.0.0.1:8000/api`). Run **Login** (or **Register**) for a portal; the request test saves `admin_token`, `captain_token`, or `client_token` for that portal’s protected calls.\n\n**Seeded users** (if you ran seeders): admin `01000000001`, captain `01000000002`, client `01000000003`, password `password`.",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"variable": [
		{ "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://127.0.0.1:8000/api" },
		{ "key": "admin_token", "value": "" },
		{ "key": "captain_token", "value": "" },
		{ "key": "client_token", "value": "" }
	],
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "Admin portal",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Register",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
									"    const j = pm.response.json();",
									"    if (j.token) pm.collectionVariables.set('admin_token', j.token);",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json", "type": "text" }],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"New Admin\",\n  \"phone\": \"01009990001\",\n  \"password\": \"password\",\n  \"password_confirmation\": \"password\"\n}"
						},
						"url": "{{baseUrl}}/admin/register"
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "Login",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"pm.test('Status is 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
									"const j = pm.response.json();",
									"pm.test('Has token', () => pm.expect(j.token).to.be.a('string'));",
									"if (j.token) pm.collectionVariables.set('admin_token', j.token);"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json", "type": "text" }],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"01000000001\",\n  \"password\": \"password\"\n}"
						},
						"url": "{{baseUrl}}/admin/login"
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "Profile (GET)",
					"request": {
						"auth": { "type": "bearer", "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{admin_token}}", "type": "string" }] },
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json", "type": "text" }],
						"url": "{{baseUrl}}/admin/profile"
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "Profile (PUT)",
					"request": {
						"auth": { "type": "bearer", "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{admin_token}}", "type": "string" }] },
						"method": "PUT",
						"header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json", "type": "text" }],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Admin Updated\"\n}"
						},
						"url": "{{baseUrl}}/admin/profile"
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "Logout",
					"request": {
						"auth": { "type": "bearer", "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{admin_token}}", "type": "string" }] },
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json", "type": "text" }],
						"url": "{{baseUrl}}/admin/logout"
					}
				}
			]
		},
